Module booking.core
Package booking.core

Class Booking

java.lang.Object
booking.core.Booking
public final class Booking extends Object
A specific booking of a Room made by a User. Has five defining characteristics:
  • The username of the user the booking is for
  • The room number of the room that is booked
  • When the booking starts
  • When the booking ends
  • The total cost of the booking
